TY  - GEN
TI  - Indicated preventive interventions for anxiety in children and adolescents: a review and meta-analysis of school based programs
AU  - S. Hugh-Jones
AU  - S. Beckett
AU  - P. Mallikarjun
PY  - 2019
UR  - https://psyarxiv.com/jadxq/
DO  - 10.31234/osf.io/jadxq
AB  - Systematic review and meta-analysis of 20 RCTs (N = 2,076): indicated (targeted) school-based anxiety programs produced a small but significant effect on self-reported anxiety at post-test (g = −0.28, 95% CI −0.50 to −0.05). Abstract truncated; details on follow-up and moderators not fully available in retrieved source. **Design:** systematic review and meta-analysis. **Limitations:** small effects; possible publication bias.
